(77454, 84937, 0, 1, 'IN FUTURE', '', '2014-07-14 00:00:00', 2000, 19, 1, 7, 'Now I''m crawling back from hell.\nBurst your mask and let this face be showed.\n\n1000times you try to hold me back.\nBut I still against the wall stand and fight.\n沉重的枷鎖被解開\n記憶失落之前最後的獨白\n\nAre you dead yet?\n\n冰冷的刀械擦出炙熱的血\n沉默的詩篇闔起嘈雜的夜\nThe world start crashing down.\nPeople are crying cause their hopes are lost.\n\n1000times you try to hold me back.\nBut I still against the wall stand and fight.\n沉重的枷鎖被解開\n記憶失落之前最後的獨白\n\n無聲的雨水靜靜飛過\n眼角的你也離開了我\n不再別過頭  \n地面濺起烏雲密布的天空\n\nYour scream I can hear  so clear.\nThe taste in the air make me suffercat.\nIn the future,everything will be fine.\nIn the future,you can find the light.\n', '', 223, '', '', '', '', 'Le''Sens Vie', '', 0, 1, 1, '2014-07-14 02:26:38', '2014-08-22 18:34:27', '2014-08-22 18:34:27'),
